üß™ 1. Escribe tu script de correcci√≥n

Gu√°rdalo como /usr/local/bin/fix-rotation.sh:

#!/bin/bash
export DISPLAY=:0
export XAUTHORITY=/home/tu_usuario/.Xauthority

xrandr --output HDMI‚Äë1 --rotate right

DEVICE="QDtech MPI7003"
TRANSFORM="0 1 0 -1 0 1 0 0 1"

for i in {1..10}; do
  if xinput list | grep -q "$DEVICE"; then
    xinput set-prop "$DEVICE" "Coordinate Transformation Matrix" $TRANSFORM
    exit 0
  fi
  sleep 1
done

exit 1

Hazlo ejecutable:

